other features of the city include the large  merkato   market  the  jan meda race ground   racecourse   bihere tsige recreation centre  and a  railway line  to  djibouti  sport facilities include  addis ababa  and  nyala stadiums
the  entoto mountains  start among the northern suburbs suburbs of the city include  shiro meda  and  entoto  in the north  urael  and  bole  home to bole international airport in the east  nifas silk  in the southeast  mekanisa  in the south and  keraniyo  and  kolfe  in the west
